Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄宿于汝名字中女神 在昆仑的守护下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.88,0:00:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿它指引你的人生 跟命中注定的人邂逅 拉娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 长老
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,05#.她的名字叫拉娜·林沁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异次元体Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如大家所知那些家伙从异次元中实体化的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能强制停止一定范围内的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.23,0:02:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说 就是发动冰冻结界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有限制者的职责是将Nova其冰冻结界中和
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作能让潘多拉活动的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.56,0:02:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冻结界吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能有全方位展开冰冻结界的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能使用和Nova相同的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 不明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 完全…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全… 但这很奇怪啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连洗礼都没有完成 居然能做到那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候只觉得必须要拼命保护学姐… 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须保护啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 莎堤莱萨学姐说什么着…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥啊 在那之後就告別了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 费了那么大劲救她 连句谢谢也没说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 这下明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点好处都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 虽然算个美人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是一帘幽梦那样的感觉我还是理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受诱惑什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但艳丽的花是有刺的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 而且是充满剧毒的刺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 学姐 正好谈到学姐的美的话题…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 我们班的男生被弄得神魂颠倒… 语无伦次…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青井和哉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话想找你谈谈 陪我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说… 学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 果然… 你的话… 貌似没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被摸了也不会有厌恶的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事头一回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…从第一次见到学姐的时候开始就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐简直就像…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉我也是头一回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道怎么形容…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能用冰冻结界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使没有EREINBAR·SET也能用冰冻结界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然能用… 但那之后几度尝试过… 完全不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让你当… 我让你当我的限制者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当真…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不能洗礼喔 如果这样也可以的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教 和哉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是West·Genetics？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真雄伟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里肯定能寻找出我命中注定的贵人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人的约定…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐难道为了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这也太多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和哉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚有空吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有空…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行… 今晚我想你来我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐的房间里…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然被邀请到她的房间我很开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她紧张成那样到底是什么事呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我已经走了多少个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 她是谁呢 没见过的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 转学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪没穿校服啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里太大了… 还以为要这样子徘徊一辈子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太夸张了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是校长室了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲切的朋友 您真是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦 不用谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能遇见像你这样的人 得感谢昆仑的女神才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.95,0:08:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昆仑？ 快到约定的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:08:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在慌啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 那禁止接触的女王…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不洗礼 跟她组队…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 象征着羁绊的圣痕也没注入这组个毛队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.02,0:09:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种暧昧的关系就只会导致你的力量被利用喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么想…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没打算正经组队的话 你还是先去主动拒绝比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事啦 现在正准备去学姐的房间赴约
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶… 赴约…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道是「进闺房」…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「初夜进闺房」  潘多拉选择了限制者的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定将其约到自己的房间进行甜蜜的老规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老规矩？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs15}（Z：你们这下知道「破鞋」一说是怎么来了的吧  =_,=）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 通过两人共度良宵  彼此间结成更深厚的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对弟弟的一种杀必死 简单来说就是进女生宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:10:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是初夜进闺房的时候到加妮沙姐姐那去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那时候喝醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后的记忆就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不给力的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:14.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说禁止接触女王居然会遵守「初夜进闺房」的规矩呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗礼都没有就利用人家大概也觉得说不过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我想你到我房间来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然学姐不见得是那种遵守规矩的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会为了我在勉为其难…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这口吗… 不 这似乎更好…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我成为你的限制者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再冷静想一次如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 现在的话还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.81,0:11:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点 一年级的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…赶时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成为莎堤莱萨的限制者那好事的一年级的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 他就是传闻中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那女王大人已经同意跟你组队啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说啊 和哉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是得恭喜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 机会难得我们来为你庆祝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长途跋涉辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天请好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果校园生活有不清楚的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都可以来问我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:12:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对下定决心送你来这里的长老们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为West·Genetics的代表表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉娜·林沁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要把他怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级想要对二年级指手画脚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他很不愿意的样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 他并没有不愿意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 不认识我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是奥德丽·德巴鲁 被叫做「斩檄的少女」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同年级「陶醉的紧缚」 竹内爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同年级「双发之牙」 托利斯·麦肯齐 好好记住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些学姐们 在嘉年华中输给了莎堤莱萨学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们做什麽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用说吗 指导啊指导
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指导对高年级生态度不好的一年级生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.31,0:13:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是我们二年级的义务呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你也过来吧 我们陪你玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么是高年级
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能允许你们胡闹！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柊 住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柊同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 被小看了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子比起指导看来更需要调教啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 动作太笨拙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这一年级的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柊… 柊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柊！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去…去找老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打小报告不是男生该做的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个坏孩子 姐姐来好好调教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是调教是指导才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:15:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么找都找不到女生宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样孩子 被姐姐踢蛋蛋的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内的坏习惯又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 一年级的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你们真扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.59,0:15:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你俩 别太过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说叫你们住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生宿舍 在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你在和谁说话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我的朋友做过分的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对… 不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昆仑之泪在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开…亚瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 要做「禁止接触的女王」的限制者?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人如果有这么棘手的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可就非常的不好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会杀掉他的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是给他身上做个「记号」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他知道过分干预危险的事情会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:17:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他个记号提醒他再也不敢看可怕的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下们要对这位大人做什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁！哪里来的乡下妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你们对这位大人出手的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才昆仑之泪告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位大人是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说些什么乱七八糟的…  这什么力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆子不小  但是和我们三人同时为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为赢得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看我！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.19,0:18:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要继续打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好… 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还… 还是这一件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你… 你啊 要人家等多久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 这么晚了真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青井和哉他？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.68,0:18:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直没有醒过来 现在在康复中心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人救了和哉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和哉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和哉的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就可以看望他了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起在这里等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 是这里的学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里如果是指这里的学校的话 还不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:19:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是要明天转到West·Genetics的 拉娜·林沁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转学生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 拉娜同学 可以稍微陪我过去一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柊说想要道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和哉他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前请一定一定先去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青井和哉的情况怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也… 也不是 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子 时不时会给身体很大的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 只是过度疲劳 没有生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来见他的吧 陪在他身边如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青井和哉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学校的转学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被长老命令「来这里寻找命中注定的贵人吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中注定的贵人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 持有昆仑之泪女性的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是昆仑之泪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣痕!? 而且还有6个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那么厉害 我觉得肯定错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉娜同学 果然是潘多拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘多拉? 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个学校有很多人有昆仑之泪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中注定的贵人也就是指限制者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 来到这个学院 一定能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:21:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我的对象的话 已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青井和哉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的命中注定的贵人除了那位大人以外没有其他了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在走廊遇到的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个莎堤莱萨学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 「禁止接触的女王」已经允许接触了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不明白那个一年级生 到底隐藏着什么力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个我对乱入进来的打扮奇怪女人更感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种各样的事情好像都变得有趣起来
